text: Moulis may refer to: ==Places== * Moulis, Ariège, a French commune in the department of Ariège * Moulis, Tarn-et-Garonne, an ancient French commune in Tarn-et-Garonne, today part of Reyniès * Moulis-en-Médoc, French commune in the department of Gironde ==People== * Danny Moulis (born 1960), Australian footballer * Pavel Moulis (born 1991), Czech footballer ==Other uses== * Moulis-en-Médoc AOC, a red wine appellation in Bordeaux, situated around the commune Moulis-en-Médoc ==See also== * Mouli (disambiguation) oc:Molins (Arièja)
title: Moulis
